OL,3,CBurnham should honour 2015 pledge to
OL,4,Cscrap tuition fees ` SNP
OL,6,FAndy Burnham should stick to his 2015
OL,7,FLabour leadership pledge and scrap
OL,8,Ftuition fees, the SNP has said.
OL,10,FAlex Kerr, the MSP for Hamilton,
OL,11,FLarkhall and Stonehouse, urged the
OL,12,Fincoming prime minister to honour the
OL,13,Fpromise he made when running against
OL,14,FJeremy Corbyn more than a decade ago.
OL,16,FMr Burnham, who is expected to succeed
OL,17,FSir Keir Starmer in the coming days,
OL,18,Fsaid at the time he would replace
OL,19,Ftuition fees with a graduate tax to
OL,20,F"lift the millstone of debt" from
OL,21,Fstudents.
OL,26,@|D@AOU|D@\O]
