OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784162882
OL,3,CBurnham should honour 2015 pledge to
OL,4,Cscrap tuition fees ` SNP
OL,6,FThe SNP said Mr Burnham should follow
OL,7,FScotland and make tuition free, which
OL,8,Fcurrently costs students south of the
OL,9,Fborder #9,790 a year.
OL,11,FThe party pointed to the recently
OL,12,Freleased National Student Survey,
OL,13,Fwhich found overall satisfaction among
OL,14,Fstudents at Scottish universities had
OL,15,Fincreased from 80.7% last year to
OL,16,F82.4% this year. However, no
OL,17,Fequivalent figure is available for
OL,18,FEngland because the overall
OL,19,Fsatisfaction question is only asked in
OL,20,Fthe devolved nations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
