OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784162882
OL,3,CBurnham should honour 2015 pledge to
OL,4,Cscrap tuition fees ` SNP
OL,6,FMr Kerr said: "In 2015, Andy Burnham
OL,7,Fsaid he would scrap tuition fees to
OL,8,F'lift the millstone of debt' from
OL,9,FEnglish students ` the cost has gone
OL,10,Fup almost every year since then, so
OL,11,Fwhy has Andy Burnham gone silent?
OL,13,F"He should copy the SNP and scrap
OL,14,Ftuition fees, otherwise he'll be off
OL,15,Fto the same start as Starmer `
OL,16,Fbreaking promises the moment he
OL,17,Fbecomes prime minister.
OL,26,@nD@OOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
