OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784162882
OL,3,CBurnham should honour 2015 pledge to
OL,4,Cscrap tuition fees ` SNP
OL,6,F"Free tuition makes a real difference
OL,7,Fin people's lives ` we know that
OL,8,FScottish graduates start their careers
OL,9,Fin #35,000 less debt on average than
OL,10,Ftheir English counterparts, an immense
OL,11,Fsaving.
OL,13,F"Andy Burnham should now honour his
OL,14,Felection pledge and lift English
OL,15,Fstudents out of tens of thousands of
OL,16,Fpounds of punishing student debt by
OL,17,Fscrapping tuition fees."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@XO]
