OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784162882
OL,3,CBurnham should honour 2015 pledge to
OL,4,Cscrap tuition fees ` SNP
OL,6,FScottish universities have in recent
OL,7,Fyears repeatedly warned about the
OL,8,Fsustainability of the current funding
OL,9,Fmodel, with hundreds of workers made
OL,10,Fredundant as part of cost-cutting
OL,11,Fmeasures.
OL,13,FEarlier this year, the Institute for
OL,14,FFiscal Studies (IFS) said the Scottish
OL,15,FGovernment may have to reconsider its
OL,16,Fpolicy of free university tuition due
OL,17,Fto mounting pressure on Holyrood's
OL,18,Fbudget, although ministers have
OL,19,Frepeatedly ruled out such a move.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784162882
OL,3,CBurnham should honour 2015 pledge to
OL,4,Cscrap tuition fees ` SNP
OL,6,FUniversities have also warned they
OL,7,Fhave become increasingly reliant on
OL,8,Fincome from international students to
OL,9,Fhelp subsidise Scots' free tuition.
OL,11,FThe IFS warned in 2024 that per-
OL,12,Fstudent funding for teaching Scottish
OL,13,Fstudents is 22% lower in real terms
OL,14,Fthan in 2013`14.
OL,16,FMr Burnham has been approached for
OL,17,Fcomment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
